Ability.Description: Using Shield prevents other Factory Remote targets from using Steal to take your Power Cores and stuns them when they use Steal on you. Movement is slower while Shielded. Vulnerable to targets using Throw while Shield is being used.

Ability.Name: Steal
Ability.Description: Able to Steal single Power Cores from Factory Remote targets. Stealing from targets will refresh the Steal ability. Stealing from targets that are using Throw will disable their abilities for 6 seconds. Using Steal against targets using Shield will cause a systems overload stunning you for 2.5 seconds.

Ability.Name: Throw
Ability.Description: Use Throw against Factory Remote targets to make them drop their Power Cores. Use Throw will reduce your Power Cores by one. Movement is slower while throwing Power Cores. Using Throw against targets that are using Shields will stun the target. Using Throw while being targeted with steal will cause you to have your Power Core pulled away and unable to use abilities for 6 seconds.

Ability.Name: Electrified Conduit
Ability.Description: When EMP Discharge damages a target, Electrified Conduit deals <<1>> additional energy damage per stack of Electrified Railgun on the target. Additionally, EMP Discharge harms up to 7 other enemy targets within 5 meters if the primary target is affected by your Electrified Railgun.

Ability.Name: Curative Jolt
Ability.Description: Kolto Infusion grants Curative Jolt, increasing the critical chance of your next Surgical Probe by 100%. This effect can only occur once every 18 seconds.

Ability.Name: Toxic Surge
Ability.Description: Weakening Blast applies Toxic Surge to the target, which causes <<1>> internal damage the next time the target takes damage from your Corrosive Grenade.

Ability.Name: Deadly Onslaught
Ability.Description: Unloads all of your ordnances in rapid succession dealing <<1>> kinetic damage and <<1>> elemental damage over the duration to up to 8 enemies. Standard and weak targets are knocked down by the blasts. Can be used while moving.

Ability.Name: Responsive Safeguards
Ability.Description: Activates an advanced response system that absorbs all incoming direct single target damage for the next 6 seconds, reflecting 50% of the absorbed damage back at the attacker and healing you for 5% of your maximum health each time an attack is absorbed. Can be used while stunned.

Ability.Name: Consuming Flames
Ability.Description: Searing Wave causes the next Immolate to deal 20% more damage.

Ability.Name: Early Ignition
Ability.Description: Mag Shot and Power Shot cause targets with a primed Thermal Detonator to combust early, dealing an additional <<1>> damage as burn over 6 seconds.

Ability.Name: Soothing Protection
Ability.Description: Force Armor grants 10 charges of Soothing Protection to the target. When Force Armor concludes, the target is healed for <<1>> health per remaining charge of Soothing Protection. Targets of your Soothing Protection will lose a charge of Soothing Protection each time you directly heal them.

Ability.Name: Impeding Slash
Ability.Description:
Lash the target with your lightsaber, dealing <<1>> weapon damage and immobilizing it for 3 seconds. When the immobilization effect ends, the target is slowed by 50% for 6 seconds.
Replaces Saber Strike.

Ability.Name: Valorous Spirit
Ability.Description: Force Mend increases your damage reduction by 15% for 6 seconds. Additionally, reduces the cooldown of Force Mend by 5 seconds.

Ability.Name: Zealous Judgment
Ability.Description: Dispatch refunds 2 focus when used on a target affected by your Pacify and can be used on any target affected by your Pacify, regardless of remaining health. Additionally, activating Pacify grants Zealous Judgment, increasing your Force and tech resistance by 75% for 6 seconds.

Ability.Name: Whirling Blade
Ability.Description:
Hurls the main-hand lightsaber at a target, dealing <<1>> weapon damage and slowing its movement speed by 50% for 3 seconds. Only usable on targets at or below 30% max health.
Replaces Dispatch.

Ability.Name: Sustaining Darkness
Ability.Description: Static Barrier grants 10 charges of Sustaining Darkness to the target. When Static Barrier concludes, the target is healed for <<1>> health per remaining charge of Sustaining Darkness. Targets of your Sustaining Darkness will lose a charge of Sustaining Darkness each time you directly heal them.

Ability.Name: Dark Echo
Ability.Description: Targets hit by Death Field have a 50% chance to emit a Dark Echo, damaging itself and up to 7 targets within 5 meters for <<1>> internal damage.

Ability.Name: Enfeebling Strike
Ability.Description:
Strike the target with your lightsaber, dealing <<1>> weapon damage and immobilizing it for 3 seconds. When the immobilization effect ends, the target is slowed by 50% for 6 seconds.
Replaces Saber Strike.

Ability.Name: Unnatural Vigor
Ability.Description: Unnatural Preservation increases your damage reduction by 15% for 6 seconds. Additionally, reduces the cooldown of Unnatural Preservation by 5 seconds.

Ability.Name: Ruthless Aggressor
Ability.Description: Vicious Throw refunds 2 rage when used on a target affected by your Obfuscate and can be used on any target affected by your Obfuscate, regardless of remaining health. Additionally, activating Obfuscate grants you Ruthless Aggressor, increasing your Force and tech resistance by 75% for 6 seconds.

Ability.Name: Extending Roar
Ability.Description: Increases the range of Force Scream to 30 meters, but Force Scream deals reduced damage beyond 10 meters. Additionally, Force Push deals 20% more damage and grants Extending Roar, allowing your next Force Scream to deal full damage regardless of the distance from the target.

Ability.Name: Bloody Mayhem
Ability.Description: Hemorrhaging Blast applies Bloody Mayhem to the target, which causes <<1>> internal damage the next time the target takes damage from your Shrap Bomb.

Ability.Name: Bootlegged Remedy
Ability.Description: Kolto Pack grants Bootlegged Remedy, increasing the critical chance of your next Emergency Medpac by 100%. This effect can only occur once every 18 seconds.

Ability.Name: Ion Wave
Ability.Description: Blasts everything in a 10-meter cone with ionized energy, dealing <<1>> elemental damage to up to 8 targets.
